# OKRs — Q2 2026 (Apr–Jun)

## O1: Establish early revenue and product-market fit
- KR1: 10 paying customers (current: 0, target: 10)
- KR2: Average time-to-first-value < 30 minutes (current: 3 days)
- KR3: Net Promoter Score > 40 (current: not measured)

## O2: Build fundraise foundation
- KR1: Series A deck finalized and reviewed by 3 advisors (current: 0%)
- KR2: 20 warm intros to Series A investors (current: 4)
- KR3: $500K in LOIs or soft commits before end of quarter (current: $0)

## O3: Scale team for Series A
- KR1: Hire founding engineer #2 (current: searching)
- KR2: Hire head of sales or first AE (current: not started)
- KR3: Advisor agreement signed with 2 domain experts (current: 1)
